{"tid":838525,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【#Cult劇】喪屍版愛·回家《小鎮滋味》(2017)(2018)","createTime":"2018-09-27T07:32:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-28T03:34:22.000Z","uid":212112,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f525b661dc1ce53de6f3b3c1b5fbd71627054612","tid":838525,"uid":212112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T07:32:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/27/152846_b87ef9fd539423bdc9059d8bb6498d8f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F27%2F152846_b87ef9fd539423bdc9059d8bb6498d8f.png&h=9fd49a2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n劇情講述一個美國中產家庭，男女主角是一對從事地產仲介的已婚夫婦並有一個剛步入青春期的女兒。某天他們的生活突然來了一埸巨變，女主角吃了污染的扇貝後居然變成了喪屍，需要靠吃人肉為生，目睹了這一切的男主角，為了讓心愛的老婆繼續&ldquo;活下去&rdquo;，在嘗盡了各種辦法後只好選擇幫助殺人。於是表面上的夫妻檔房地產仲介從此成為業業的夫妻檔殺手，充滿懸疑色彩同時荒誕爆笑的情節不斷上演⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/27/152849_d4d8c61600c2414d668641b6c8af65ab.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F27%2F152849_d4d8c61600c2414d668641b6c8af65ab.png&h=7d0b3d85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nNetflix旗下連續劇，喪屍為主線，但幾乎每個場景和細節都透露著清新和溫情。女主角變異之後不僅整個人精神煥發，夫婦之間的床邊話，乃至整個家庭會議的談話，都是圍繞著吃人殺人，都是漫不經心似乎像是平常小事。女主角變成喪屍跟常人沒有什麽分別，跟普通人一樣在同一張餐桌吃飯，都用刀叉碗碟，只是她的碟上是的切割好的人的肢體。跟普通人一樣用攪伴機，只是攪出來的是鮮紅的血漿奶昔。跟普通人一樣用雪櫃藏凍肉，只是藏的凍肉是冷冰冰的死屍。跟普通人一樣上班，只是上班時偶爾眼睛會掉，手指會斷。<br />\n一個美國小鎮上的普通家庭，有一天妻子突然變成了無人肉不歡的活死人。這樣的開頭，怎麽往下接都可以，陰謀與血腥的蔓延，懸疑與真相的追逐，都能很有意思。但Netflix這次偏偏劍走偏鋒，把本劇打造成小品式血腥溫情倫理處境喜劇，30分鐘一集輕輕鬆鬆，我一看就停不了下來，一口氣就連續看完兩個season並超級期待下一個season來臨 。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/27/152851_8b01298cc61fa484f28040efbf2dd18a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F27%2F152851_8b01298cc61fa484f28040efbf2dd18a.png&h=2f2d5f20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n提得一提，當年的E.T童星Drew Barrymore已年屆中年，她在劇中一邊吃人一邊流露出超級無辜的眼神，當真越老越肥越可愛！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/27/152854_e032d71e3322c35b131e23c771ee48cd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F27%2F152854_e032d71e3322c35b131e23c771ee48cd.png&h=e651469f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/27/152856_b56b5303138a8e91bc3e4f7c53f0d3a7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F27%2F152856_b56b5303138a8e91bc3e4f7c53f0d3a7.png&h=c746606f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/p/BnuUgPkBJaM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fp%2FBnuUgPkBJaM%2F&d=ponsyYfsuH7%2BR%2BoRpLuOkzANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=f4835e3c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fp%2FBnuUgPkBJaM%2F&h=9a9ffff9\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/p/BnuUgPkBJaM/</a>"},{"pid":"3d21571d268d05d7114ad78134debea162e6eee5","tid":838525,"uid":212112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T07:47:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba6d00f3f6227c0942dce4cd5efb4e980bed8db4","tid":838525,"uid":212112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T08:28:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23f474161e974ac3476a3c280c690921be3fbcda","tid":838525,"uid":212112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T09:20:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0d3f8bafd99ebc7595405fca3e965a2a88123f8","tid":838525,"uid":182372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T11:30:36.000Z","msg":"好似幾過癮 但有排追<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3d264ed81b16283a4aa771dd3c4967f69970202","tid":838525,"uid":212112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0d3